We should be allowed to laugh at normatives and commonalities without being made into hateful bigots. I understand on reddit that extreme sexism and women hatred is common - but this is not a symbol of that.

As someone for social justice (and a proud feminist myself)... you can lose your humanity if you start to care about theory, micro-analyzing and policing language, and go looking for things to be offended by.
